<m:mo> = </m:mo>
</m:math>
 its weight, acting downward
</item>
<item> 
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> N </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
</m:math>
 normal force on block – 2 due to the surface of table, acting upward
</item>
<item> 
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> T </m:mi>
<m:mn> 1 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
</m:math>
 tension in the string, towards left   
</item>
<item> 
<m:math>
