<m:mi> T </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
</m:math>
 tension in the string, towards right   
</item>
</list>
</para>
<para id="element-25">We note here that “mass-less” string passes over a “mass-less” pulley and no friction is involved. As such, the tensions in the string on either side of the pulley are equal.
</para>
<para id="element-26">
The forces on the block – 3 are :
</para>
<para id="element-27">
<list id="list-27" list-type="enumerated"><item> 
<m:math>
<m:msub>
